audi australia has given undertakings to the court that it will not make representations to the effect that a motor vehicle in the audi q7 series is available for purchase for, or from, an advertised price when: a) the specified motor vehicle is not available for purchase for, or from, the advertised price; b) there is a fee or charge to be paid in addition to that advertised price and the existence of the additional fee or charge is not identified; or c) there is a fee or charge to be paid in addition to that advertised price for particular features of the advertised motor vehicle and the existence of the additional fee or charge is not identified.
